OL,4,Ccriticises police handling of case
OL,6,FThe mother of a trainee barrister who
OL,7,Fwent missing on a Spanish island has
OL,8,Fcriticised British police for their
OL,9,Fhandling of the case.
OL,11,FBen Ross, from Wigan, disappeared in
OL,12,Fthe tourist hotspot Palma City in
OL,13,FMajorca on Wednesday 10 July.
OL,15,FHe travelled to the island to take a
OL,16,Fbreak from studying to become a
OL,17,Fbarrister in Manchester.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/12
