OL,6,FHome Office protocol states that if
OL,7,Fsomeone goes missing while abroad, you
OL,8,Fshould phone your local police force
OL,9,Fwho subsequently contact the police
OL,10,Fforce in the relevant country through
OL,11,FInterpol - the International Criminal
OL,12,FPolice organisation.
OL,14,FHowever, when Ben's mum Felix Robinson
OL,15,Farrived in Majorca on Saturday 20
OL,16,FJuly, she was told by Interpol that
OL,17,FGreater Manchester Police (GMP) had
OL,18,Fnot reported Ben's disappearance,
OL,19,Fdespite her giving multiple statements
OL,20,Fto officers.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/12
