OL,4,Ccriticises police handling of case
OL,6,FMs Robinson believes this has left the
OL,7,Fsearch for the missing 26-year-old,
OL,8,Fwho has been missing for more than a
OL,9,Fweek, severely delayed, Spanish police
OL,10,Funaware and the British Consulate
OL,11,Fpowerless.
OL,13,FA family spokesperson said: "Felix has
OL,14,Fspent days trying to get local
OL,15,Fauthorities to take her reports of a
OL,16,Fmissing person seriously.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/12
