OL,4,Ccriticises police handling of case
OL,6,F"In the UK, the policies around
OL,7,Freporting missing people in a
OL,8,Fdifferent country, require local
OL,9,Fpolice to inform Interpol who will
OL,10,Fthen activate police in the country of
OL,11,Fthe missing person.
OL,13,F"Initially, local police did not take
OL,14,Fher report seriously. Believing that
OL,15,Fit was a case of a 26-year-old young
OL,16,Fman living his best life out in Spain.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/12
