OL,3,CMother of man missing in Majorca
OL,4,Ccriticises police handling of case
OL,6,F"They closed the case down twice and
OL,7,Feven closed a complaint in which Ben's
OL,8,Fmum begged a Sergeant to take the case
OL,9,Fseriously, knowing what a vulnerable
OL,10,Fstate he is in due to having all his
OL,11,Fpossessions stolen and nowhere to
OL,12,Fstay."
OL,14,FITV Granada Reports understands that
OL,15,FGMP did contact Interpol following the
OL,16,Freports Ben was missing and continues
OL,17,Fto provide assistance where it can.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/12
