OL,6,FBen decided to extend his stay in
OL,7,FMajorca and move into a temporary
OL,8,Frental after finding a local job, his
OL,9,Fmum said.
OL,11,FHowever, her son had his phone,
OL,12,Fpassport, keys and wallet stolen while
OL,13,Fhe was going for a swim at the beach
OL,14,Fon Saturday 6 July.
OL,16,FSpeaking on behalf of Ms Robinson, the
OL,17,Fspokesperson added: "Ben went to the
OL,18,Flocal police station to report the
OL,19,Ftheft, after several hours in the
OL,20,Fstation, he left and attempted to find
OL,21,Fthe apartment he was staying in.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/12
