OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F397A1721679231
OL,3,CMother of man missing in Majorca
OL,4,Ccriticises police handling of case
OL,6,F"After becoming lost, due to only
OL,7,Fstaying on the island for a matter of
OL,8,Fweeks, he eventually found the
OL,9,Fapartment in the late hours of that
OL,10,Fday.
OL,12,F"Despite knocking, his flatmates
OL,13,Fdidn't let him in and in a distressed
OL,14,Fstate, Ben broke the lock to gain
OL,15,Fentry.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/12
