OL,4,Ccriticises police handling of case
OL,6,F"The following days with his flatmates
OL,7,Fwere tough as tensions about the
OL,8,Fbroken door developed, despite his
OL,9,Fpromising to pay for the damages
OL,10,Fcaused under the extenuating
OL,11,Fcircumstances."
OL,13,FMs Robinson tried to arrange a bank
OL,14,Ftransfer for Ben on 10 July to support
OL,15,Fhimself financially after losing all
OL,16,Fof his possessions.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/12
