OL,4,Ccriticises police handling of case
OL,6,FThe spokesperson continued: "Upon
OL,7,Freturning to the flat, Ben's mental
OL,8,Fhealth had declined and the distress
OL,9,Fof what was going on caused him to cut
OL,10,Fcommunications with his mum.
OL,12,F"Like most parents of young adults,
OL,13,FFelix believed after a day or two that
OL,14,Fher son would be back in touch.
OL,15,FUnfortunately, this did not happen.
OL,17,F"Felix received a distressed email
OL,18,Fclaiming to be from Ben on a new email
OL,19,Faddress due to not being able to
OL,20,Faccess any of his existing accounts.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/12
