OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F397A1721679231
OL,3,CMother of man missing in Majorca
OL,4,Ccriticises police handling of case
OL,6,F"The email told her what had happened
OL,7,Fand that he was not interested in what
OL,8,Fhappened next to him, which has left
OL,9,FFelix seriously concerned for her son.
OL,11,F"Despite previous reports claiming
OL,12,Ftheir homicide team were looking for
OL,13,FBen already, this has transpired to
OL,14,Fnot be the case due to GMP's repeated
OL,15,Ffailures to activate the Interpol
OL,16,Fprotocols."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/12
