OL,6,FWorrying about the significant costs
OL,7,Fof travel during the school holiday
OL,8,Fand the peak British holiday season,
OL,9,Ffriends of Ms Robinson have set up a
OL,10,FGoFundMe page to help support her
OL,11,Fcover the costs of the search for her
OL,12,Fson.
OL,14,FThe crowdfunder created on Wednesday
OL,15,F16 July has now reached nearly #4,000.
